---
// src/components/Pricing.astro
---
<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200" id="pricing">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-blue-600 font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-4">
        Transparent Pricing
    </h2>
    <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">
        One Investment. <br>
        <span class="text-blue-600">Infinite Traffic.</span>
    </h3>
    <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Build an asset you own. No hidden monthly maintenance fees. Just pure performance.
    </p>
</div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto items-start">
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-lg relative flex flex-col h-full hover:border-blue-300 transition-colors">
                <div class="mb-6">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">The Launchpad</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-2 min-h-[32px]">Perfect for new businesses needing a professional start.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-6 flex items-baseline gap-1">
                    <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">RM 2,800</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs font-medium">One-time</span>
                </div>

                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-slate-700">
                        <i data-lucide="layout" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span><strong>High-Impact Single Page Site</strong></span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-slate-700">
                        <i data-lucide="zap" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Lightning Fast & Secure Hosting</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-slate-700">
                        <i data-lucide="trending-up" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span><strong>10 Programmatic SEO Pages</strong> Included</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-slate-700">
                        <i data-lucide="message-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Direct-to-WhatsApp Setup</span>
                    </li>
                     <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-slate-700">
                        <i data-lucide="smartphone" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Mobile Responsive Design</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <a href="#contact" class="w-full block text-center bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 text-slate-600 font-bold py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors text-sm">
                    Build Launchpad
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-6 border border-slate-800 shadow-2xl relative flex flex-col h-full transform lg:-translate-y-4 z-10">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-blue-600 text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-xl uppercase tracking-wider">
                    Most Popular
                </div>

                <div class="mb-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Market Dominator</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs mt-2 min-h-[32px]">The "Full Stack". A complete authority site + The massive growth engine.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-6 flex items-baseline gap-1">
                    <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">RM 4,800</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs font-medium">One-time</span>
                </div>

                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-white font-medium">
                        <i data-lucide="layout-template" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                        <div>
                            <strong>3-Page Official Website</strong>
                            <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs font-normal mt-0.5">(Home, About, Services)</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
                        <i data-lucide="globe" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span><strong>50+ Programmatic SEO Pages</strong></span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
                        <i data-lucide="zap" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Lightning Fast & Secure Hosting</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
                        <i data-lucide="message-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Direct-to-WhatsApp Setup</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
                        <i data-lucide="smartphone" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Mobile Responsive Design</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
                        <i data-lucide="search" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Technical SEO & Schema Setup</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <a href="#contact" class="w-full block text-center bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors text-sm">
                    Dominate Local Search
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-cyan-200 shadow-lg relative flex flex-col h-full">
                <div class="mb-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-cyan-900">Sidecar</h3>
                        <span class="bg-cyan-200 text-cyan-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Add-on Engine</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-cyan-700/80 text-xs mt-2 min-h-[32px]">Already have a website? Plug this engine in for traffic.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-6 flex items-baseline gap-1">
                    <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-cyan-900">RM 2,200</span>
                    <span class="text-cyan-600 text-xs font-medium">One-time</span>
                </div>

                <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-cyan-800">
                        <i data-lucide="globe" class="w-4 h-4 text-cyan-600 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span><strong>50+ Programmatic SEO Pages</strong></span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-cyan-800">
                        <i data-lucide="server" class="w-4 h-4 text-cyan-600 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Hosted on Independent Server</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-cyan-800">
                        <i data-lucide="message-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-cyan-600 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span><strong>WhatsApp Conversion Funnel</strong></span>
                    </li>
                     <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-cyan-800">
                        <i data-lucide="shield-check" class="w-4 h-4 text-cyan-600 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>100% Safe (No Login Needed)</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-cyan-800">
                        <i data-lucide="bar-chart-3" class="w-4 h-4 text-cyan-600 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Monthly Traffic Reporting</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <a href="#contact" class="w-full block text-center bg-white border-2 border-cyan-200 text-cyan-700 font-bold py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-cyan-50 hover:border-cyan-300 transition-colors text-sm">
                    Add Engine Only
                </a>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-blue-100">
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <i data-lucide="info" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Domain Ownership
            </h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-blue-800/80 leading-relaxed">
                To ensure you maintain 100% ownership of your brand, <strong>the custom domain name (e.g., yourbusiness.com) is provided by you</strong>. 
                If you are new to this, we can assist with the purchase process, but you will hold the account and ownership.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>